sent | Evernorth Health Services</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>Project Management Principal:</strong> GRC point of contact for CIP, GI&amp;O, and Audit. Oversees identification, reporting, tracking, and remediation of vulnerabilities, findings, and technology debt.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h3>2017 ‚Äì 2023 | Wells Fargo</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>SVP &amp; Senior Manager, Technology Operations:</strong> Led Leadership &amp; Performance Reporting, Program Management &amp; Platform Strategy for Commercial Finance Capital Markets. Managed Incident, Problem, Change, and Release. Built Emergency Vulnerability Management Team resolving 17 critical zero-day issues with 100% closure.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h3>2015 ‚Äì 2017 | GE Capital</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>Operations Leader:</strong> Led 24-person ops team ensuring 24/7/365 stability of Wintel/Unix infrastructure. Oversaw vulnerability management, vendor escalation, and performance monitoring.</li>\n    <li><strong>Service Delivery Manager:</strong> Directed application performance, governance, customer satisfaction, and continual service improvement.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h3>2010 ‚Äì 2013 | GE Capital</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>Senior Program Manager:</strong> Managed company-wide client technology programs across U.S. and Canada. Introduced handheld tech for sales, increasing speed and deal closure.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h3>2007 ‚Äì 2010 | GE Capital</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>Senior Program Manager:</strong> Delivered risk reduction and process-improvement projects, including $250K infrastructure initiatives.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h3>2004 ‚Äì 2007 | Altria Corporate Services</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>Senior Program Manager:</strong> Managed WAN &amp; Internet connectivity for Altria, Philip Morris, and Kraft NA. Delivered global datacenter connectivity and supported financial communications transitions.</li>\n    <li><strong>Senior Solutions Architect:</strong> Designed global IT solutions including shared services datacenters, global help desk, and ITIL-driven service management.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h2>Education</h2>\n  <hr>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>MBA, Information Decision Technology Management</strong> ‚Äî Iona University</li>\n    <li><strong>BS, Criminology</strong> ‚Äî Long Island University</li>\n    <li><strong>MS Degree in Public Administration</strong> ‚Äì Long Island University, Dobbs Ferry, NY</li>\n  </ul>\n\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','About','','publish','closed','closed','','about','','','2025-12-12 16:21:35','2025-12-12 21:21:35','',0,'https://randomcategory.com/?page_id=872',0,'page','',0),(885,1,'2025-04-25 21:52:19','2025-04-26 01:52:19','','img_4547.jpg','','inherit','open','closed','','img_4547-jpg','','','2025-04-25 21:52:19','2025-04-26 01:52:19','',0,'http://andresanz.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2025/04/img_4547.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(886,1,'2025-04-25 21:52:28','2025-04-26 01:52:28','','img_4546.jpg','','inherit','open','closed','','img_4546-jpg','','','2025-04-25 21:52:28','2025-04-26 01:52:28','',0,'http://andresanz.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2025/04/img_4546.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(887,1,'2025-04-25 21:52:40','2025-04-26 01:52:40','','img_4545.jpg','','inherit','open','closed','','img_4545-jpg','','','2025-04-25 21:52:40','2025-04-26 01:52:40','',0,'http://andresanz.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2025/04/img_4545.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(888,1,'2025-04-25 21:52:59','2025-04-26 01:52:59','','img_4547-1.jpg','','inherit','open','closed','','img_4547-1-jpg','','','2025-04-25 21:52:59','2025-04-26 01:52:59','',0,'http://andresanz.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2025/04/img_4547-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(891,1,'2025-04-25 22:06:53','2025-04-26 02:06:53','','img_4484.jpg','','inherit','open','closed','','img_4484-jpg','','','2025-04-25 22:06:53','2025-04-26 02:06:53','',0,'http://andresanz.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2025/04/img_4484